<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/criminal-procedure-rule-committee> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Criminal Procedure Rules govern the way criminal cases are managed, and set out the processes of the criminal courts. Criminal Procedure Rule Committee is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Justice ."@en .
